    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Airship is an open platform for playing multiplayer indie games.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BedWars 2</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BedWars 2 is currently in early testing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why did we make BedWars 2 on Airship?</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free kits (no 70%+ tax)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Much more advanced anticheat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Better networking to improve combat responsiveness</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modern game engine for more powerful creator tools</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Better servers (with region control!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A clean slate for a fresh BedWars experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381730/extras/454aac5a553487cc196a9129032fcfcd.avif?t=1764878911\" width=616 height=356 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381730/extras/6b39fdb278dd0d1175b6b00146757727.avif?t=1764878911\" width=1600 height=840 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become a Developer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We make multiplayer easy with Unity Engine and TypeScript. The Client &amp; API is even open source! Check out our website for details on how to create a game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381730/extras/29bf22a6c6ed308c68424b01747c99e8.avif?t=1764878911\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381730/extras_big/29bf22a6c6ed308c68424b01747c99e8.webp?t=1764878911 width=1600 height=983 /></span></p>",
